-- Hastoe Capital Said to Plan U.K. Bond Investor Meetings
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-03-09T14:24:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-09/hastoe-capital-said-to-plan-u-k-bond-investor-meetings.html
Hastoe Capital Plc plans to hold
meetings with bond investors in the U.K. starting March 14,
according to a banker with knowledge of the arrangements.  RBC Capital Markets and  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  are organizing
the meetings, the banker said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
